    <published>2020-02-01T06:13:13.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-03-14T03:25:13.913Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="准备工作"><a href="#准备工作" class="headerlink" title="准备工作"></a>准备工作</h1><ul><li>Git</li><li>Live2d的模型(后面会发)<h1 id="下载Live2d插件"><a href="#下载Live2d插件" class="headerlink" title="下载Live2d插件"></a>下载Live2d插件</h1>先检查有没有装live2d插件，如何查看插件是否安装了呢？<br>打开根目录下的”package.json”文件，查看里面有没有”hexo-helper-live2d”<br>如果有，请重新安装live2d：<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm unistall hexo-helper-live2d</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-helper-liv2d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>然后去”node_modules”文件夹里面查看有没有一个叫做”live2d-widget”的文件夹。<br>如果有，就安装成功了。<h1 id="下载模型并配置-model"><a href="#下载模型并配置-model" class="headerlink" title="下载模型并配置(model)"></a>下载模型并配置(model)</h1>去github<a href="https://github.com/xiazeyu/live2d-widget-models.git" target="_blank" rel="noopener">下载</a>大佬的模型<br>下载完了以后把packages里面的随便一个文件夹复制到”node_modules”文件夹里。</li></ul><p>复制完以后打开根目录下的”_config.yml”<br>拉到最底下复制粘贴</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">live2d:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  pluginModelPath: assets&#x2F;</span><br><span class="line">  model:</span><br><span class="line">    use: live2d-widget-model-epsilon2_1  #模板目录，在node_modules里</span><br><span class="line">  display:</span><br><span class="line">    position: right</span><br><span class="line">    width: 150 </span><br><span class="line">    height: 300</span><br><span class="line">  mobile:</span><br><span class="line">    show: false  #是否在手机进行显示</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="预览"><a href="#预览" class="headerlink" title="预览"></a>预览</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看Live2d效果</p><p>(我是不会告诉你们我的是其他版的:D)</p>]]></content>
    
